---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Inguz Care ‚Äî Residential Children‚Äôs Homes"
  description="Safe, nurturing homes with tailored support plans."
>
  <!-- HERO with background image -->
  <section class="relative">
    <div class="relative h-[60vh] md:h-[70vh]">
      <img
        src="/hero.jpg"
        alt="Carer and children completing a colourful jigsaw puzzle together"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 h-full flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-white text-center md:text-left max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Compassionate, outcomes-focused residential care
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
            We provide safe, nurturing homes with tailored support plans,
            helping young people grow, learn, and thrive.
          </p>

          <!-- Centered CTA buttons -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[#3d5756]"
            >
              Refer / Contact us
            </a>
            <a
              href="/our-homes"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-[#5f7c7b] text-[#5f7c7b] font-semibold hover:bg-[#eef5f4] bg-white/90"
            >
              Explore our homes
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR VALUES -->
  <section id="values" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center">Our Values</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-slate-600">Tap a value to read more.</p>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <!-- 1) Safety First -->
        <details class="rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:outline-none">
            <div class="aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Safety First</h3>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">(tap to expand)</span>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-3">
            <p class="font-medium">
              Our promise: We create predictable, nurturing routines where children feel protected and calm.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Consistent boundaries and trauma-aware care, 24/7.</li>
              <li>Well-trained staff, clear safeguarding practice, and calm spaces.</li>
              <li>We notice early signs of worry and act quickly and kindly.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- 2) Belonging & Warmth -->
        <details class="rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:outline-none">
            <div class="aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3">üè†</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Belonging &amp; Warmth</h3>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">(tap to expand)</span>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-3">
            <p class="font-medium">
              Our promise: This is a home‚Äîchildren are known, accepted, and cared for as individuals.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Stable relationships and a family-style atmosphere.</li>
              <li>Celebrations of culture, identity, and milestones.</li>
              <li>House traditions that build trust and togetherness.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- 3) Voice & Choice -->
        <details class="rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:outline-none">
            <div class="aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3">üó£Ô∏è</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Voice &amp; Choice</h3>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">(tap to expand)</span>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-3">
            <p class="font-medium">
              Our promise: Children shape their day, their plans, and their future with real say.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Everyday choices (meals, activities, room d√©cor) that build confidence.</li>
              <li>Care plans written with the child, not just about them.</li>
              <li>Honest feedback loops‚Äîwhat you say changes what we do.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- 4) Growth for Life -->
        <details class="rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100 focus:outline-none">
            <div class="aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-center">
              <span class="text-5xl mb-3">üå±</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Growth for Life</h3>
              <span class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">(tap to expand)</span>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-3">
            <p class="font-medium">
              Our promise: We nurture strengths and skills that last well beyond our front door.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
              <li>Education, hobbies, and life skills (from homework to cooking).</li>
              <li>Step-by-step independence with the right support at the right time.</li>
              <li>Goals reviewed often so progress is visible and celebrated.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
